# QuickBite Delivery Performance Analysis Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project analyzes delivery performance and customer experience for a food delivery application called QuickBite.

## Business Problem
The company faced issues with delivery delays and inconsistent partner performance across cities.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Google Sheets
- Data Visualization

## Key Insights
- Identified cities with highest delivery delays
- Evaluated delivery partner performance
- Analyzed rating distribution and payment modes
- Provided insights to improve operational efficiency and customer satisfaction

